1
00:00:00,773 --> 00:00:03,983
Let's spend a little time just settling on the breath.

2
00:00:44,344 --> 00:00:46,472
developing metta in the particular.

3
00:00:48,259 --> 00:00:51,773
Bring to mind and into your heart a benefactor.

4
00:01:27,409 --> 00:01:31,513
Bring to mind and into your heart all those who are near and dear to you.

5
00:02:07,808 --> 00:02:12,907
Bring to mind and into your heart friends, workmates, even good acquaintances.

6
00:02:48,747 --> 00:02:51,956
Bring to mind and into your heart a neutral person.

7
00:03:27,965 --> 00:03:31,596
turn the stream of goodwill towards ourselves.

8
00:04:07,537 --> 00:04:18,642
bringing to mind and into that heart of goodwill someone whom we find difficult, remembering that here lies the gateway to universal, unconditional love.

9
00:04:54,922 --> 00:04:57,170
having developed our metta in the particular.

10
00:04:58,235 --> 00:05:03,918
Let us radiate it outwards, first of all, to all those who are here with us now.

11
00:05:39,995 --> 00:05:44,841
to all those in this district, whether they live wholesome or unwholesome lives.

12
00:06:20,730 --> 00:06:22,523
to all those in our country.

13
00:06:58,817 --> 00:07:00,372
To all who live in Europe,

14
00:07:37,141 --> 00:07:38,629
to all people on earth.

15
00:08:09,540 --> 00:08:14,581
Offering Metta to all beings in the six directions.

16
00:08:16,307 --> 00:08:18,437
All beings before us.

17
00:08:54,293 --> 00:08:57,029
all beings behind us.

18
00:09:32,649 --> 00:09:34,458
All beings to our left.

19
00:10:09,285 --> 00:10:10,841
all beings to our right.

20
00:10:45,735 --> 00:10:47,798
all beings below us.

21
00:11:22,725 --> 00:11:24,871
all beings above us.

22
00:11:59,783 --> 00:12:03,043
and to all beings in all directions.

